{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "通往舞會的邀請函", "storyInfo": "祥子從莫菲絲的口中得知睦的夢境並不簡單。“睦”在這個夢裡得到了自己想要的人生，為此拒絕了嘗試拯救她的祥子，將其推下了山崖。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g6_rmbtmine", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "nrun"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "nrun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……呼……唔……！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_airshiptakeoff", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "machine"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "machine", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "machine", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉悶的聲音在空曠的洞穴中迴盪，那是附近仍未停止作業的掘地機發出的聲響。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣溫越來越低。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑出洞穴的那一刻，寒意同時到來。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而寒冷，只會讓她心臟的跳動不斷加快。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該……該怎麼面對她？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法開口，無法面對。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖嘖，該如何是好呢？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無須回頭，她已然知道來者是誰。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子的夢境，我真的很滿意呢~", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢城堡的職責就是讓每個孩子都有一場好夢，我一一實現了她的願望。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到這個夢境這麼穩定地運轉——不，甚至完美無缺，完全超出了我的預期。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且在這裡，有一些很有趣的事情正在發生哦。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你在欺騙她。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，這才不算是欺騙呢。我和她交易了很多次，她很清楚我的身分。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到這個結果，我也很開心呢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算意識到是夢境，依舊不願意離開，那不就說明我的造夢技藝無人能比嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1937_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_yingying_ked_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（贊同的哼唧聲）", "name": "卡爾頓們"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1937_1#3$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，最後來的竟然是……？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還蠻有趣的呢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就不打擾你們了~豐川祥子，相信你很快也會發現這個夢境的有趣之處。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shdwblwvr", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子，大家都在等你呢，我們回去吧。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回去哪裡？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看著莫菲絲消失，卻一點都不驚訝……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的一切，都是我們虛構出來的。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們”？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，不屬於我們。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g9_warmrabbitnest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electricguitar", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，你彈得好棒！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥……", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，媽媽……祥，她跑去哪裡了？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小祥？可能跑去其他地方了吧……？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#6$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，不對。祥……祥她不可能丟下我。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#6$3"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡呼的人群突然變得一片死寂，所有人都目不轉睛地看著睦。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，你好像忘記了——", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不是你一個人的夢。", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是“我們”的夢。", "name": "“睦的母親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們”。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這個夢境裡，每一個“睦”都有機會實現自己的願望。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們和小睦一起，構建出了只屬於我們的美夢——大家都能得到幸福的夢。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們存在於小睦的腦海中，觀看了無數遍她的人生。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，我們一致認為，對於所有的“睦”來說，這就是最好的結局——", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，豐川祥子，你是這個美夢的敵人。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，你到底在說什麼？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不希望你繼續痛苦下去，但是我們都不應該繼續躲在這樣的夢裡——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，小睦能在這裡幸福地生活下去，這才是最重要的事。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和大家不一樣，我想和祥子好好談談。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以留在這裡，和我一起，守護小睦的美夢。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦是一個脆弱的孩子，她可能還無法決定，到底是醒來，還是就這樣幸福下去。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你也選擇留在這裡，幫我們一起讓這個夢持續下去，那夢境自然就會變成“現實”。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是“現實”唯一的基準，你就是“現實”。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，留下來吧，祥子。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拒絕。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……拒絕？", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦現實中的身體正躺在冰冷的夢城堡裡，你覺得這樣的結局也是好的嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的愛她，就不會做出這種事情。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能讓小睦開心，只要我們都能存在——是不是現實又有什麼關係？！", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我擁有小睦的所有記憶，我知道你心裡最需要什麼！", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你願意留在這裡，我甚至能給你一個完整的Ave{@nbs}Mujica！", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴！你根本就不是睦……睦才不會這樣說話。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡你，也喜歡小睦……", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼要讓我陷入兩難？", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“動手。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫名的聲音盤旋在兩人的頭頂上。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“動手，動手，動手。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠方的山脈好像在震動，地上的碎石也有節奏地跳動了起來。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“動手。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周圍明明沒有其他人，祥子卻覺得好像有無數雙眼睛正在盯著自己。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“動手——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#12$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說得對，我們對小睦來說就是無數的影子。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#12$3"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了讓影子能一直躲在黑暗裡，再微弱的光也要抹去。", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#12$3"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“睦”一點一點地將祥子逼到了懸崖邊。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#5$2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你想做什麼？！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#5$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#12$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子……", "name": "“睦”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#12$3"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“睦”伸出了手，將手放在了祥子的肩膀上。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "CameraShake", "